trans-unit.source: Represents the root element of an XML document containing the results of all files written when the <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll(System.String,System.String)" /> method is invoked.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta l'elemento di primo livello di un documento XML contenente i risultati di tutti i file scritti quando Ã¨ stato richiamato il metodo <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll(System.String,System.String)" />.

trans-unit.source: When you invoke the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method, all resolved discovery documents and a file containing a map of all those files are saved to a directory.
trans-unit.target: Quando si richiama il <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> (metodo), documenti di individuazione e un file contenente una mappa di tutti questi file vengono salvati tutti risolti in una directory.

trans-unit.source: The map file is described in XML with the root element being <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.DiscoveryClientResultsFile>; this class is passed to the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> class to serialize the results.
trans-unit.target: Viene descritto il file di mappa in XML con l'elemento radice da <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.DiscoveryClientResultsFile>; questa classe viene passata per il <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> classe per serializzare i risultati.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.DiscoveryClientResultsFile" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza della classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.DiscoveryClientResultsFile" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResultCollection" /> containing the results from a <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ReadAll(System.String)" /> or <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll(System.String,System.String)" /> invocation.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResultCollection" /> contenente i risultati di una chiamata a <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ReadAll(System.String)" /> o a <see cref="M:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll(System.String,System.String)" />.
